      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-cnf-imp-000      thru acc-cnf-imp-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-key    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-key-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-key-reg-110.
       acc-key-reg-900.
