           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac      .
           divide    w-lin-num-lin-vis    into w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac      .
           multiply  w-lin-num-lin-vis    by   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac      .
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-cor-nrg-dac      .
